library(numbers)
test <- 1
noget <- 1:28
length(noget[(28 %% noget)==0])
result <- FALSE
while(!result){
  test <- test + 1
  testing <- 1:test
  result <- length(testing[(test %% testing)==0]) > 500
}
test
